data.description: Welcome to this modern 3-bed, 2-bath home in Hollywood Lakes! The captivating residence features a spacious backyard perfect for a pool. With an exceptional open floor plan, generous bedrooms, and a delightful kitchen, this home offers comfort and style. Additional highlights include a 1-car garage, no HOA, and strategic proximity to the beach, highways, downtown Hollywood, and FLL Airport. Ideal for boat owners, designated parking and ramp access are available and Golf Enthusiast,  Explore this must-see property seamlessly blending functionality with style.
